{
  "stem": "4764.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And to the best of my ability, I've managed to-- to overcome them, I think, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I'm happy with my lot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm happily married now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My wife is a fantastic woman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I'm not only saying this because she's going to watch this, but because she is.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She's also helped me to raise my children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because when we were married, they were still very young.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It wasn't easy for her to come into a situation like she came in, with three children from, from somebody else.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she's done a fantastic job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I'm-- I, I don't think I could have done it without her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I mean, I tried for a few years on my own.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I think they wouldn't have turned out the way they have, if she hadn't helped me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She's a very intelligent and able woman who understands [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the problems.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It's one thing to, to tell a child off if you're the parent, another to tell it if you're the stepparent.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They don't tolerate that very well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I know it's not right, but that's the way human nature is.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I think we're over the worst of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I think that the, the children are hopefully now on their way that they can fend for themselves.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I can perhaps now relax.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If there are, I've some-- I think I've suppressed quite a bit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I feel there's something still in my mind which, as we've been talking this afternoon, it hasn't come out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'm not sure why I've suppressed it.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
